</span><span _ngcontent-ng-c1845019670="">Innovation &amp; Commercialisation</span></span></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c1845019670="" class="content is-small is-sans my-0"> How to drive cooperation on AI and transfer research results into products </p></a></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c1845019670="" class="column is-3"><a _ngcontent-ng-c1845019670="" tabindex="0" routerlink="/site/compute-climate" routerlinkactive="is-active" class="nav-item-link has-text-light ghost" href="/en/site/compute-climate"><figure _ngcontent-ng-c1845019670="" class="is-fullwidth nav-item-media is-default"><img _ngcontent-ng-c1845019670="" loading="lazy" src="./assets/images/portals/carbon-md.png" alt="AI carbon" class="is-inline-block" style="background-image: url('./assets/images/portals/carbon-small.png');"></figure><p _ngcontent-ng-c1845019670="" class="is-size-4 mb-2 mt-5 pt-1"><span _ngcontent-ng-c1845019670="" class="is-fullwidth"><span _ngcontent-ng-c1845019670="" class="icon-text"><span _ngcontent-ng-c1845019670="" class="icon"><i _ngcontent-ng-c1845019670="" class="fas fa-chevron-right is-size-6 has-text-success"></i></span></span><span _ngcontent-ng-c1845019670="">AI Compute and the Environment</span></span></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c1845019670="" class="content is-small is-sans my-0"> AI computing capacities and their environmental impact. </p></a></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c1845019670="" class="column is-3"><a _ngcontent-ng-c1845019670="" tabindex="0" routerlink="/site/health" routerlinkactive="is-active" class="nav-item-link has-text-light ghost" href="/en/site/health"><figure _ngcontent-ng-c1845019670="" class="is-fullwidth nav-item-media is-default"><img _ngcontent-ng-c1845019670="" loading="lazy" src="./assets/images/portals/ai-health-md.jpg" alt="AI &amp; Health" class="is-inline-block" style="background-image: url('./assets/images/portals/ai-health-small.jpg');"></figure><p _ngcontent-ng-c1845019670="" class="is-size-4 mb-2 mt-5 pt-1"><span _ngcontent-ng-c1845019670="" class="is-fullwidth"><span _ngcontent-ng-c1845019670="" class="icon-text"><span _ngcontent-ng-c1845019670="" class="icon"><i _ngcontent-ng-c1845019670="" class="fas fa-chevron-right is-size-6 has-text-success"></i></span></span><span _ngcontent-ng-c1845019670="">AI &amp; Health</span></span></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c1845019670="" class="content is-small is-sans my-0"> AI can help health systems overcome their most urgent challenges. </p></a></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c1845019670="" class="column is-3"><a _ngcontent-ng-c1845019670="" routerlink="/site/ai-futures" routerlinkactive="is-active" class="nav-item-link has-text-light ghost" href="/en/site/ai-futures"><figure _ngcontent-ng-c1845019670="" class="is-fullwidth nav-item-media is-default"><img _ngcontent-ng-c1845019670="" loading="lazy" src="./assets/images/portals/foresight-md.png" alt="" class="is-inline-block" style="background-image: url('./assets/images/portals/foresight-small.png');"></figure><p _ngcontent-ng-c1845019670="" class="is-size-4 mb-2 mt-5 pt-1"><strong _ngcontent-ng-c1845019670="" class="is-fullwidth"><span _ngcontent-ng-c1845019670="" class="icon-text"><span _ngcontent-ng-c1845019670="" class="icon"><i _ngcontent-ng-c1845019670="" class="fas fa-chevron-right is-size-6 has-text-success"></i></span></span><span _ngcontent-ng-c1845019670="">AI Futures</span></strong></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c1845019670="" class="content is-small is-sans my-0">AI’s potential futures.</p></a></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c1845019670="" class="column is-3"><a _ngcontent-ng-c1845019670="" tabindex="0" routerlink="/work-innovation-productivity-skills" routerlinkactive="is-active" class="nav-item-link has-text-light ghost" href="/en/work-innovation-productivity-skills"><figure _ngcontent-ng-c1845019670="" class="is-fullwidth nav-item-media is-default"><img _ngcontent-ng-c1845019670="" loading="lazy" src="./assets/images/wips-md.png" alt="" class="is-inline-block" style="background-image: url('./assets/images/wips-small.png');"></figure><p _ngcontent-ng-c1845019670="" class="is-size-4 mb-2 mt-5 pt-1"><strong _ngcontent-ng-c1845019670="" class="is-fullwidth"><span _ngcontent-ng-c1845019670="" class="icon-text"><span _ngcontent-ng-c1845019670="" class="icon"><i _ngcontent-ng-c1845019670="" class="fas fa-chevron-right is-size-6 has-text-success"></i></span></span><span _ngcontent-ng-c1845019670="">WIPS</span></strong></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c1845019670="" class="content is-small is-sans my-0"> Programme on Work, Innovation, Productivity and Skills in AI. </p></a></div></div></div></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c1845019670="" class="navbar-dropdown navbar-dropdown--large"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1845019670="" class="container m-b-xxl"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1845019670="" class="columns is-multiline"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1845019670="" class="column is-3 is-offset-3"><a _ngcontent-ng-c1845019670="" tabindex="0" routerlink="/ai-toolkit/get-started" routerlinkactive="is-active" class="nav-item-link has-text-light ghost" href="/en/ai-toolkit/get-started"><figure _ngcontent-ng-c1845019670="" class="is-fullwidth nav-item-media is-default"><img _ngcontent-ng-c1845019670="" loading="lazy" src="./assets/images/ai-policy-toolkit-md.jpg" alt="" class="is-inline-block" style="background-image: url('./assets/images/ai-policy-toolkit-small.jpg');"></figure><p _ngcontent-ng-c1845019670="" class="is-size-4 mb-2 mt-5 pt-1"><strong _ngcontent-ng-c1845019670="" class="is-fullwidth"><span _ngcontent-ng-c1845019670="" class="icon-text"><span _ngcontent-ng-c1845019670="" class="icon"><i _ngcontent-ng-c1845019670="" class="fas fa-chevron-right is-size-6 has-text-success"></i></span></span><span _ngcontent-ng-c1845019670="">AI Policy Toolkit</span></strong></p><p _ngcontent-ng-c1845019670="" class="content is-small is-sans my-0"> Map your AI policy landscape, identify priorities and explore policy examples </p></a></div><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1845019670="" class="column is-3"><a _ngcontent-ng-c1845019670="" tabindex="0" routerlink="/catalogue/overview" router